      <title>随着战争风险的增加，泽连斯基要求修建新的防御工事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/zelenskiy-calls-for-new-fortifications-amid-fears-war-may-expand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽伦斯基呼吁在基辅的反攻陷入停滞以及担心俄罗斯可能试图占领更多领土的情况下加快建立主要防线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/zelenskiy-calls-for-new-fortifications-amid-fears-war-may-expand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 10:27:55 GMT</pubDate>
