    <item>
      <title>美国“鱼鹰”飞机在日本岛附近坠毁 至少一人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/at-least-one-killed-in-us-osprey-aircraft-crash-off-japan-island</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据日本共同社援引日本海岸警卫队的消息报道，周二，一架美军鱼鹰飞机坠入日本西南部屋久岛附近海域，造成至少一人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/at-least-one-killed-in-us-osprey-aircraft-crash-off-japan-island</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 10:08:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列总统将于战后首次出访阿联酋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/israel-s-president-due-in-uae-in-first-foreign-trip-since-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几位知情人士表示，以色列总统艾萨克·赫尔佐格计划本周晚些时候快速访问迪拜，参加 COP28，即联合国气候谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/israel-s-president-due-in-uae-in-first-foreign-trip-since-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 10:05:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉押注巴西对气候的关注将在 COP28 上抢尽风头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/lula-bets-brazil-s-pivot-on-climate-will-steal-the-show-at-cop28</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统将把注意力集中在亚马逊雨林上，并推出重大新政策，以表明博尔索纳罗时代后回归绿色目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/lula-bets-brazil-s-pivot-on-climate-will-steal-the-show-at-cop28</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 10:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
